    <data key="d0">National Australia Bank Automated Compliance &amp; Deployment Framework</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7V8wTCkjOqo</data>
    <data key="d2">An automated compliance validation engine that evaluates non-prod pipeline build metadata against relational regulatory rules before promoting artifacts to production environments.</data>
